channel.title: ~IceRealm Reborn~ Project
channel.description:
Hello fellow MoparScapers, I am back and have decided to start up a project.
This is the topic where I am going to recruit fellow programmers to help on my project.
If you would like to apply for a position use this layout:
[code] Msn name: Programming experience: Proof: [/code]
Current Positions open:
Head Programmers: Iceman primadude codeusa
Bug Tester's: ______ ______ ______
People with Idea's: ______ ______ ______ ______
IceRealm Reborn is based off of ZDR.
Final project will be cleaned up and will have features no one has ever thought of. To apply, follow the basic layout listed above.
Current Idea's Incompleted are in red, completed are in green: Pocket Teleport in the music sidebar fully functioning with text and teleport ability Shops in quest list completed and are unable to be opened in combat or in wilderness
Pics: [IMG]http://i37.tinypic.com/2uh9wth.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i33.tinypic.com/2r5ajus.png[/img]
NOTE: I haven't taken too much time to create this post so picture's and so forth will come shortly.
